{"tid":420482,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"見到條女去蒲好唔開心","createTime":"2017-10-01T12:20:21.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-02T04:13:08.000Z","uid":145244,"like":13,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"294a394f07bcb561f4006156c60b9ee2850956db","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"同佢一齊嘅時候佢應承過我唔會去玩，我都同佢講我唔想佢去埋啲煙花之地。近排佢個friend失戀，佢問我批准佢琴日陪個friend飲酒傾計，話唔係去玩，只係飲嘢，之後佢去咗蘭桂坊。<br />\n<br />\n我原本都擔心佢自己飲酒，因為佢份人無節制，怕佢飲多左所以話陪佢去，但係佢話人哋失戀冇理由帶埋男朋友去（個friend我都認識）。最後佢同三個中學同學一齊去，兩女一男，叫做有報告行蹤，但係我都係怕佢危險就話出去接佢。凌晨三點幾去到蘭桂坊，入到去佢嗰間野，見到個個喺度跳舞，見到佢除咗同啲中學同學一齊之外仲有兩個搭訕識嘅男仔，企喺度睇左佢一陣，見到佢哋幾個黐埋一齊影相，我條女個樣係玩得開心。<br />\n<br />\n果下我即刻嬲咗，行埋去俾佢知道我嚟咗，俾咗個屌你老母嘅眼神就走左。佢呢返出嚟，同我講佢有同人哋講佢有男朋友，佢冇玩。<br />\n<br />\n其實我知道佢冇帽我嘅，因為佢都知道我嚟緊接佢，但係見到佢着好少布（佢話過唔會着個件衫出街）去啲咁嘅地方，仲要有人過嚟同佢地搭訕一齊影相，個心真係唔好受。最大嘅問題係本來佢應承我只係飲嘢傾計，但係去咗啲場個個勁歌熱舞，仲要飲醉。佢話本來真係飲嘢，係個friend話去嗰個場，但係佢ig Snapchat post嘅野都見到佢好投入。<br />\n<br />\n其實係咪個個見到自己女朋友去咗啲咁嘅地方，得咁少布，都會好唔開心？我好愛佢，佢平時都好好，我知佢冇出軌，但係一諗起佢玩嘅樣就好唔開心。"},{"pid":"819dd0f1f3279f00fb704bf56551078fcdccd6b0","tid":420482,"uid":21310,"like":30,"dislike":2,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:22:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fb2fdb2292962484e42d8a8d30543b88dd916da0","tid":420482,"uid":76005,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:22:58.000Z","msg":"養唔精 就中出即飛喇<br />\n遲早帽事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253c9ebea8a16ce290f1b5f94b31d0590b834c3f","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:24:48.000Z","msg":"公道講句佢平時對我係好好嘅，佢都應該冇同人跳舞或者點，係我見到佢係嗰啲地方又咁yo真係不爽囉"},{"pid":"b1ec04516d04b792b193fd46c8cc96ae2723d261","tid":420482,"uid":69295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:27:05.000Z","msg":"掛左個(已售)名牌未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"392cf9d2f495229df70acf8976e36de60dadc078","tid":420482,"uid":21961,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:27:08.000Z","msg":"呢d女根本未撚玩夠<br />\n佢家下認死狗 佢d frd都會比返說話佢聽<br />\n「聽去玩下都唔等？」 <br />\n「咁樣條仔即係唔信你啦」<br />\n「著咩衫都管？」<br />\n條女只係會認為要為左氹下你低聲下氣兩句<br />\n但只要個心有癮/比frd講多兩句都要走出去玩"},{"pid":"eac6c07d23cc4d1f8c815195a6f6121d47075f2d","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:27:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>掛左個(已售)名牌未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話有同人講有男朋友"},{"pid":"979a6b917f927ffc763a8d211f02ca46070e88b6","tid":420482,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:30:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>掛左個(已售)名牌未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話有同人講有男朋友</blockquote><br />\n咁咪姐係話俾入聽 屇完無手尾"},{"pid":"dd6ceac0f9544b161f103cd84b2f9e010e325bc3","tid":420482,"uid":46042,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:31:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>掛左個(已售)名牌未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話有同人講有男朋友</blockquote><br />\n咁咪姐係話俾人聽 屌完無手尾</blockquote>"},{"pid":"3fcc3152cb804dd1a8403e4a811fce2835e960b2","tid":420482,"uid":1585,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:32:53.000Z","msg":"on撚9,玩都唔撚比"},{"pid":"34b1642178d3aa02674ee4c9d0690cbf79b3e589","tid":420482,"uid":116989,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:32:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女根本未撚玩夠<br />\n佢家下認死狗 佢d frd都會比返說話佢聽<br />\n「聽去玩下都唔等？」 <br />\n「咁樣條仔即係唔信你啦」<br />\n「著咩衫都管？」<br />\n條女只係會認為要為左氹下你低聲下氣兩句<br />\n但只要個心有癮/比frd講多兩句都要走出去玩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 講得太好"},{"pid":"419880d990ac8a36abfe3f317c62f6d09f26b9d5","tid":420482,"uid":25319,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:33:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>呢d女根本未撚玩夠<br />\n佢家下認死狗 佢d frd都會比返說話佢聽<br />\n「聽去玩下都唔等？」 <br />\n「咁樣條仔即係唔信你啦」<br />\n「著咩衫都管？」<br />\n條女只係會認為要為左氹下你低聲下氣兩句<br />\n但只要個心有癮/比frd講多兩句都要走出去玩</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8322d002accee63765023c82d3c5a58d3ccfe350","tid":420482,"uid":86999,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:35:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>掛左個(已售)名牌未呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢話有同人講有男朋友</blockquote><br />\n有男朋友呀 班狗咪更加落力追你條女囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我建議你唔好叫佢唔好做咩咩咩<br />\n你同佢講 你鐘意去邊就去邊 着咩就着咩<br />\n唔好成日搵佢 唔好咁關心佢<br />\n如果你女朋友真係好似你講到咁好既<br />\n佢一定會做為段感情做返d野<br />\n可能佢會為左你而唔使你提都會唔做你唔鐘意既野<br />\n如果唔係既 咪當慢慢放低佢"},{"pid":"c9de82a04d8580247021f0a75bccc14e0378ba8a","tid":420482,"uid":72567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"想問下一齊左幾耐 點識 你地有冇ex"},{"pid":"d4d14e3e87244953640269295dfed4b8d9f8f0dc","tid":420482,"uid":75692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:40:56.000Z","msg":"中出即飛"},{"pid":"da53817d4f1bc9ab08c95488eaf1cb86cb0b6771","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:41:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>想問下一齊左幾耐 點識 你地有冇ex</blockquote><br />\n五個月<br />\n算係學校有啲聯繫加埋朋友介紹所以識<br />\n我o3佢o2"},{"pid":"e354574a2c8b0dd2ec0f9458bf77de28c9ac69db","tid":420482,"uid":2419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:42:03.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"4a9aedb06515456d43f64434ac2db7823075f2d0","tid":420482,"uid":47722,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:48:19.000Z","msg":"飛啦，臭雞嚟，佢唔會因為你而唔玩，依加唔飛就等戴帽啦"},{"pid":"d5c5aa8f7cd5dd983ac3e0647bea786565facc65","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>飛啦，臭雞嚟，佢唔會因為你而唔玩，依加唔飛就等戴帽啦</blockquote><br />\n咁佢又真係問過我先去嘅，只不過本身話傾計飲嘢，我expect係佢哋幾個friend自己圍內吹水，唔會咁樣"},{"pid":"0ee9fc5c8034485d5406bd4c2cde6034cdf211b8","tid":420482,"uid":2419,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:57:00.000Z","msg":"btw想問下屌你老母既眼神係點樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ef6b6b9dea6e144e5560234c114a23c541c343b","tid":420482,"uid":21961,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T12:57:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>飛啦，臭雞嚟，佢唔會因為你而唔玩，依加唔飛就等戴帽啦</blockquote><br />\n咁佢又真係問過我先去嘅，只不過本身話傾計飲嘢，我expect係佢哋幾個friend自己圍內吹水，唔會咁樣</blockquote><br />\n去到呢個位真係睇你自己<br />\n你覺得可以當冇野咪由佢去<br />\n大時大節陪frd落去<br />\n過唔到自己個關早散早著<br />\n5個月過眼雲煙者"},{"pid":"332c491fdbae87b96c3f1701cea19e277831fda0","tid":420482,"uid":89577,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:01:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>on撚9,玩都唔撚比</blockquote><br />\n咁講啦，假設你係樓主女友，講啲唔講啲，又唔撚自制，係嗰啲地方比人溶撚左我睇下你條死臭雞仲講唔講到呢句嘢出黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死臭雞</span>"},{"pid":"fd87d0f758edec46576d5858aa579c0881c96aae","tid":420482,"uid":100100,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:02:14.000Z","msg":"我個ex都係會落去蒲 飲酒 <br />\n係人都唔會鐘意自己條女去玩 <br />\n小心比人帽左都唔知<br />\n我之前有次，佢話同啲fd去飲酒，之後比我睇到有條仔問佢攞左電話仲明溝佢，仲要我個ex一直同人地whatsapp，正臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n小小忠告: 條女未撚玩夠，就唔好放咁多心機落去，轉個頭帽左都唔知"},{"pid":"a744ffaedacdb15de0ed80521d12fb4c3355d8a5","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:03:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>飛啦，臭雞嚟，佢唔會因為你而唔玩，依加唔飛就等戴帽啦</blockquote><br />\n咁佢又真係問過我先去嘅，只不過本身話傾計飲嘢，我expect係佢哋幾個friend自己圍內吹水，唔會咁樣</blockquote><br />\n去到呢個位真係睇你自己<br />\n你覺得可以當冇野咪由佢去<br />\n大時大節陪frd落去<br />\n過唔到自己個關早散早著<br />\n5個月過眼雲煙者</blockquote><br />\nChing講得啱 真係睇我自己 佢平時對我好好 第一次又係俾咗我 我都好愛佢 唔會想同佢分手 佢琴日都喊住同我道歉叫我唔好唔要佢 <br />\n<br />\n但係一諗起真係控制唔到自己唔開心 所以上嚟同大家訴下苦"},{"pid":"93344d5663dc49751c3b1444334c0af99ed66656","tid":420482,"uid":145244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-01T13:04:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>on撚9,玩都唔撚比</blockquote><br />\n咁講啦，假設你係樓主女友，講啲唔講啲，又唔撚自制，係嗰啲地方比人溶撚左我睇下你條死臭雞仲講唔講到呢句嘢出黎<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">死臭雞</span></blockquote><br />\nChing真係明白事理 其實我嬲有好大部份嘅原因都係我好擔心佢"}]}